wikipedia_page.main: Janet Ryder (born 21 June 1955) is a Welsh politician.  She was a Plaid Cymru member of the National Assembly for Wales for North Wales from 1999 to 2011. She moved with her family to Wales in 1990 and has since learnt Welsh.
